"""Follow stream without overflowing terminal.

Requires "colorama" and ANSI escape code support.

Seems like "less" should be able to do this but I couldn't see how :(

## TODO:

  - copy output to file
  - time how long command/line takes

"""
# pylint: disable=line-too-long

# Test Cases for Long Line Handling:
#
#   $ cat follow.py | python3 follow.py
#
# 1111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111
# 2222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222222
# 
# 
